---
import DocsLayout from "../../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
const alloyPipeline = [
    "discovery.kubernetes \"pods\" {",
    "  role = \"pod\"",
    "  namespaces = [\"aiops\"]",
    "}",
    "",
    "discovery.relabel \"pods_logs\" {",
    "  targets = discovery.kubernetes.pods.targets",
    "  rule {",
    '    source_labels = ["__meta_kubernetes_pod_label_app"]',
    '    target_label  = "app"',
    "  }",
    "}",
    "",
    "loki.source.kubernetes \"pod_logs\" {",
    "  targets = discovery.relabel.pods_logs.output",
    "  forward_to = [loki.write.default.receiver]",
    "}",
    "",
    "loki.write \"default\" {",
    "  endpoint {",
    "    url = \"http://loki.aiops.svc.cluster.local:3100/loki/api/v1/push\"",
    "  }",
    "}",
].join("\n");
---
<DocsLayout
    title="Loki y Grafana Alloy - ITOps Automation Lab"
    description="Phase 4 del Rocky Linux ITOps Automation Lab: Loki para agregacion de logs y Grafana Alloy para recoleccion — el pipeline de observabilidad de logs."
    activePage="loki-grafana-alloy"
    lang="en"
    prev={{ label: "Prometheus y Alertmanager", href: "/en/aiops-lab/phase-4/prometheus-alertmanager" }}
    next={{ label: "Grafana Dashboards", href: "/en/aiops-lab/phase-4/grafana-dashboards" }}
>
    <div class="docs-page">
        <div class="f4-hero"><div class="f4-hero__top"><div class="f4-hero__badge">Phase 4.3</div><span class="f4-hero__time">Loki + Alloy</span></div><h1 class="f4-hero__title">Loki y Grafana Alloy<span class="f4-hero__accent"> · Logs</span></h1><p class="f4-hero__subtitle">Loki almacena logs con el mismo modelo de labels que Prometheus usa para metricas. Grafana Alloy (sucesor de Promtail) los recolecta de cada pod via Kubernetes API. Juntos forman el pipeline de observabilidad de logs.</p></div>

        <div class="overview-section">
            <div class="section-header"><span class="section-num">01</span><h2 class="overview-h2">Loki: La Base de Datos de Logs</h2></div>
            <p class="overview-lead">Loki es un sistema de agregacion de logs diseniado para ser eficiente en storage. A diferencia de Elasticsearch, no indexa el contenido de los logs — solo indexa los labels (app, namespace, pod). El texto se comprime y almacena en chunks.</p>
            <div class="specs-grid">
                <div class="spec-card"><div class="spec-card__val">31 dias</div><div class="spec-card__label">Retencion</div></div>
                <div class="spec-card"><div class="spec-card__val">10 Gi</div><div class="spec-card__label">PVC Storage</div></div>
                <div class="spec-card"><div class="spec-card__val">boltdb-shipper</div><div class="spec-card__label">Storage Backend</div></div>
                <div class="spec-card"><div class="spec-card__val">filesystem</div><div class="spec-card__label">Object Store</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card"><div class="info-card__icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg></div><div class="info-card__text"><strong>En Oracle Cloud, Loki usa OCI Object Storage como backend.</strong> El archivo <code>configmap-oci.yml</code> contiene la configuracion S3-compatible. En el lab local, el backend es filesystem sobre PVC. La migracion es transparente para los queries.</div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="overview-section">
            <div class="section-header"><span class="section-num">02</span><h2 class="overview-h2">Alloy: Recoleccion de Logs</h2></div>
            <p class="overview-lead">Grafana Alloy es el sucesor de Promtail. Corre como DaemonSet — un pod por nodo — y recolecta logs de todos los contenedores. Usa la API de Kubernetes para descubrir pods y enriquecer los logs con labels.</p>
            <div class="code-block"><div class="code-block__header"><span class="code-block__file">alloy/configmap.yml — pipeline River</span></div>
                <pre><code>{alloyPipeline}</code></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="flow-row">
                <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-step__label">Kubernetes API</div><div class="flow-step__desc">Alloy descubre pods en el namespace aiops</div></div>
                <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
                <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-step__label">Relabeling</div><div class="flow-step__desc">Extrae labels: app, namespace, pod, container</div></div>
                <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
                <div class="flow-step"><div class="flow-step__label">Push a Loki</div><div class="flow-step__desc">POST /loki/api/v1/push con los logs etiquetados</div></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="overview-section">
            <div class="section-header"><span class="section-num">03</span><h2 class="overview-h2">Query de Logs desde Grafana</h2></div>
            <p class="overview-lead">Loki usa LogQL, un lenguaje de queries similar a PromQL. Los logs se exploran desde Grafana con el datasource de Loki preconfigurado.</p>
            <div class="terminal-block"><div class="terminal-block__bar"><div class="terminal-block__dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div><span class="terminal-block__title">LogQL queries</span></div><div class="terminal-block__body">
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-comment"># Todos los logs del namespace aiops</span></div>
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-out"><span class="t-ok">{'{'}</span>namespace="aiops"}</span></div>
                <div class="t-line t-line--spacer"></div>
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-comment"># Logs de error de un pod especifico</span></div>
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-out">{'{namespace="aiops", app="n8n"}'} |= "error"</span></div>
                <div class="t-line t-line--spacer"></div>
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-comment"># Conteo de errores por app en las ultimas 2h</span></div>
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-out">sum by(app) (count_over_time({'{namespace="aiops"}'} |= "error" [2h]))</span></div>
            </div></div>
            <p class="overview-text">El workflow 2 de n8n (Log Analysis) usa exactamente estas queries via la API HTTP de Loki. Cada hora consulta logs de error, los procesa con LLM y envia un reporte a Discord.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="overview-section overview-section--cta">
            <div class="cta-card"><div class="cta-card__content"><h3 class="cta-card__title">Siguiente: Grafana Dashboards</h3><p class="cta-card__desc">Con metricas en Prometheus y logs en Loki, Grafana unifica la visualizacion. Dashboards preconfigurados con panels de cluster, SLOs y estado de servicios.</p></div><a href="/en/aiops-lab/phase-4/grafana-dashboards" class="cta-card__btn"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.5 2v6h-6M2.5 22v-6h6M2 11.5a10 10 0 0118.8-4.3M22 12.5a10 10 0 01-18.8 4.2"/></svg>Grafana</a></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</DocsLayout>

<style is:global>
    .docs-page { max-width: 740px; }
    .f4-hero { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.875rem; padding: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .f4-hero__top { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .f4-hero__badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--green-300); padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 0.4rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .f4-hero__time { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--text-dim); padding: 0.35rem 0.65rem; border-radius: 0.4rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
    .f4-hero__title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-50); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .f4-hero__accent { color: var(--green-500); font-weight: 500; }
    .f4-hero__subtitle { font-size: var(--text-md); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 560px; }
    .overview-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; } .overview-section--cta { margin-top: 1rem; }
    .section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
    .section-num { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--green-600); font-weight: 500; }
    .overview-h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-xl); font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-50); margin: 0; }
    .overview-lead { font-size: var(--text-base); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 560px; }
    .overview-text { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .specs-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .spec-card { text-align: center; padding: 0.75rem 0.5rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.6rem; }
    .spec-card__val { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-400); margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
    .spec-card__label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-3xs); color: var(--text-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
    .info-card { display: flex; gap: 0.65rem; padding: 0.875rem 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.6rem; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .info-card__icon { flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--green-400); margin-top: 0.1rem; }
    .info-card__icon svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; display: block; }
    .info-card__text strong { color: var(--green-50); font-weight: 600; }
    .info-card__text code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; color: var(--green-300); }
    .code-block { background: #0a0a0a; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.6rem; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .code-block__header { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0.45rem 0.85rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.025); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .code-block__file { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-2xs); color: var(--text-dim); }
    .code-block pre { margin: 0; padding: 0.85rem; overflow-x: auto; }
    .code-block code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.55; }
    .flow-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .flow-step { flex: 1; text-align: center; }
    .flow-step__label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-300); margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
    .flow-step__desc { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.4; }
    .flow-arrow { color: var(--green-500); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .terminal-block { background: #0a0a0a; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.6rem; overflow: hidden; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .terminal-block__bar { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.025); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .terminal-block__dots { display: flex; gap: 0.3rem; }
    .terminal-block__dots span { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); display: block; }
    .terminal-block__title { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: var(--text-2xs); margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; padding-right: 2.5rem; }
    .terminal-block__body { padding: 0.65rem 0.85rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.1rem; }
    .t-line { line-height: 1.5; } .t-line--spacer { height: 0.35rem; }
    .t-out { color: var(--text-dim); padding-left: 0; }
    .t-ok { color: var(--green-400); }
    .t-comment { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); font-style: italic; }
    .cta-card { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.75rem; }
    .cta-card__content { flex: 1; }
    .cta-card__title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-base); font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-50); margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
    .cta-card__desc { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.55; margin: 0; }
    .cta-card__btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 500; color: var(--green-50); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; }
    .cta-card__btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-color: var(--border-hover); }
    @media (max-width: 700px) { .specs-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } .flow-row { flex-direction: column; } .flow-arrow { display: none; } }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .cta-card { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; } }
</style>
